<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="controversial-adj">controversial <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌkɒntrə'vɜːʃl/    美 /ˌkɑːntrə'vɜːrʃl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>引起争论的； 有争议的</strong></h4>
<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Whether the buildings in this area should be pulled down has remained <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (有争议的); people are still looking for other possible solutions.  （2012 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. controversial  </p></div>